=== delayed_001 | delayed | Burns warmup steps before counting payload 1 down to zero
# family: delayed
# variant: 001
# initial warmup register: 2
# initial payload register: 1
# intended use: compare short and long budgets
# small bound note: tiny budgets can miss the halt
# medium bound note: the witness appears after warmup
# large bound note: the verdict stays HALTS
# ranking hint: warmup and payload both decrease
# output note: stage counts the warmup region
# checkpoint note: mirror tracks the payload region
# branch note: branch adds a tiny detour in the main loop
# analyst question: where does UNKNOWN disappear?
# expected shape: staging loop then payload loop
set warmup 2
set payload 1
set ticks 0
set checksum 1
set stage 0
staging:
jz warmup main
sub warmup 1
add stage 1
jump staging
main:
copy mirror payload
jz payload done
add ticks 1
sub payload 1
copy mirror payload
jnz mirror branch
jump main
branch:
nop
jump main
done:
out stage
out ticks
out checksum
halt
=== end

